author: Jessica Bennett
title: Kenya Moore: I’ll Give You $1 Million If You Can Prove My Breast Are Fake!
text:
February 24, 2017 by Jessica Bennett 0 Shares Advertisement 
While a few stars of The Real Housewives of Atlanta have admitted to going under the knife , Kenya Moore claims her hot body is 100% God-given and gym-maintained. 
She’s even willing to put her money where her mouth is, offering up a million bucks to one troll if she could prove her boobs aren’t the real thing. 

Kenya recently posted a photo of herself alongside fellow “housewife” Kandi Burruss, with one fan calling Kandi’s tatas real and Kenya’s fake. 
The former beauty queen responded calmly, taking it as a compliment while revealing she’s simply wearing a corset bra that lifts the girls up where they belong. 
A post shared by Kenya Moore (@thekenyamoore) on Feb 23, 2017 at 3:07pm PST 
Another fan then responded more harshly, calling Kenya a liar and recalling a past episode where Kenya’s doctor confirmed her breasts were fake. 
The actress quickly replied, saying the fan must have heard the episode incorrectly, offering her $1M if she can pinpoint the episode and moment the doctor said she had “breast implants.” 

“If you can show me where the doctor said “breast implants,” I will give you $1M. And bitch u know I have it. LOL” 
A post shared by The Shade Room (@theshaderoom) on Feb 23, 2017 at 7:26pm PST 
On an episode of Watch What Happens Live , Kenya admitted her chest doesn’t always look real because it’s the first place she loses and gains weight. 
“They get bigger as I'm aging. If I gain, like, two pounds, it's going to my boobs. It's crazy. I'm, like, going up in a bra size lately.” 

Do you believe Kenya is all natural? Sound off below. 

The Real Housewives of Atlanta Season 9 airs Sundays at 8 p.m. ET on Bravo.
